# OkCupid Web API – fill after reverse engineering
# Base URL (usually https://www.okcupid.com or API subdomain)
OKCUPID_API_BASE=https://www.okcupid.com
# OKCUPID_API_HOST=https://api.okcupid.com

# Browser User-Agent (copy from DevTools → Network → request headers)
# OKCUPID_USER_AGENT=Mozilla/5.0 ...

# Auth: paste cookie name=value pairs (one per line) or use a token if the API uses one
# OKCUPID_COOKIES=session=xxx; auth_token=yyy
